{"title":"【071】CSS边框综合案例","slug":"hell0-world19","date":"2022-10-04T03:22:59.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:18:08.944Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world19.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"        css边框案例      正方形<br>","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"ie=edge\">\n  <title>css边框案例</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../case-2.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"square1\">正方形</div><br>\n    <span id=\"more\"></span>\n    样式中给元素设置的宽高，是不包含该元素边框宽高的，它只包含元素内容的宽高。<br><br>\n    <div id=\"square2\">正方形</div><br><br>\n    <div id=\"triangle1\">三角形</div>\n    <div id=\"triangle2\">三角形</div><br><br>\n    <div id=\"trapezium\"> 梯形</div><br><br>\n    <div id=\"windmills\"> \n      <div class=\"box1\"></div>\n      <div class=\"box2\"></div>\n      <div class=\"box3\"></div>\n      <div class=\"box4\"></div>\n    风车</div><br><br>\n  </body>\n  </html>","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}